---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy — Noise Decibel Meter';
const description = 'Noise Decibel Meter privacy policy. We process all audio locally in your browser. No sound data is ever sent to a server. No cookies, no tracking, no personal data collected.';
const canonicalUrl = 'https://noisedecibelmeter.com/privacy-policy';
---

<style>
  html[data-dark] .page-title  { color: #f2f2f2 !important; }
  html[data-dark] .page-date   { color: #555 !important; }
  html[data-dark] .page-h2    { color: #f2f2f2 !important; }
  html[data-dark] .page-body  { color: #888 !important; }
  html[data-dark] .highlight-box { background: #1a1a1a !important; border-color: #272727 !important; }
  html[data-dark] .highlight-text { color: #f2f2f2 !important; }
</style>

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}>
  <main style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 24px 96px;">

    <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:#888;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;margin:0 0 16px;">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="page-title" style="font-size:40px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-1.8px;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 12px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="page-date" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:#888;margin:0 0 48px;">Last updated: June 2025</p>

    <!-- TL;DR highlight -->
    <div class="highlight-box" style="background:#fafafa;border:1px solid #ebebeb;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <p class="highlight-text" style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;margin:0 0 8px;">The short version</p>
      <p class="page-body" style="font-size:15px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">
        We do not collect, store, or transmit your audio. All microphone processing happens locally in your browser using the Web Audio API. We do not use cookies, we do not run advertising trackers, and we do not sell data — because we have none to sell.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">1. Information we collect</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 12px;">
      <strong>Audio / microphone data:</strong> Noise Decibel Meter requests access to your microphone solely to measure sound levels. Raw audio samples are processed in real time inside your browser using the Web Audio API. No audio data is ever transmitted to our servers or any third party, and nothing is stored on disk.
    </p>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      <strong>Usage data:</strong> We do not use analytics cookies or third-party tracking scripts. Standard web server access logs (IP address, browser user-agent, page URL, timestamp) may be retained for up to 30 days for security and abuse-prevention purposes, then automatically deleted. These logs are never sold or shared.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">2. Cookies and local storage</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      We use <code style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:14px;background:#f5f5f5;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;">localStorage</code> to remember your dark-mode preference. This data never leaves your device and contains no personally identifiable information. We do not set advertising or analytics cookies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">3. Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      The site is served via a CDN/hosting provider. Their infrastructure may log standard access data as described above. We do not embed social-media widgets, advertising networks, or analytics services that track you across websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">4. Data retention</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      Because we do not collect personal data, there is nothing to retain beyond the transient server access logs mentioned above (deleted after 30 days). CSV exports you generate are saved directly to your device; we never see their contents.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">5. Children's privacy</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      This service is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so we can delete it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">6. Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 32px;">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="page-h2" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#171717;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">7. Contact</h2>
    <p class="page-body" style="font-size:16px;color:#4d4d4d;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">
      Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact" style="color:#171717;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;">Contact us</a> and we'll respond within a few business days.
    </p>

  </main>
</Layout>
